{"tid":910112,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"支那快被TRUMP打殘！報道指支那計劃加大開放市場！","createTime":"2018-11-21T02:09:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-21T08:57:24.000Z","uid":79563,"like":29,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"b3e2bffd344d2dfe3e895ce5e460e367a7057b39","tid":910112,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T02:09:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1429316-20181120.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1429316-20181120.htm&d=ALGqpQX7p98fRTqHuUgWuPiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=2a664273\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1429316-20181120.htm&h=b86c3c4e\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1429316-20181120.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n美支領導人月底在阿根廷二十國集團峰會會晤前，有消息指，支那醞釀再度加大開放市場，希望為貿易戰降溫。<br />\n<br />\n路透社引述支那消息指，支那多個相關部委正參與制定政策措施，預計將於下月慶祝國家改革開放40周年儀式時公布，措施包括降低關稅和放寬貿易限制等。<br />\n<br />\n消息指，支那按自己的步伐開放市場。對於美支能否在短期內達成協議持審慎態度。"},{"pid":"c06cfac7cefdbe5aba64c82b6d726689ea308320","tid":910112,"uid":150347,"like":35,"dislike":1,"score":34,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T02:16:51.000Z","msg":"又拖時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 都要人地肯信先得架"},{"pid":"dfa5070532f93250dd106cf6c4f51f1a53ec5ff7","tid":910112,"uid":93986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T02:18:01.000Z","msg":"又話堅持到底"},{"pid":"944812a4b8a638c0f130f8d0571d59172c4e8625","tid":910112,"uid":79563,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"c06cfac7cefdbe5aba64c82b6d726689ea308320","tid":910112,"uid":150347,"like":35,"dislike":1,"score":34,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T02:16:51.000Z","msg":"又拖時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 都要人地肯信先得架"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T02:39:51.